Comment: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.97,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Opening Skit ===
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:07.97,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Mei-chan, you've really become someone we can count on lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:08.84,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.84,0:00:12.42,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It seems my sister also places a great deal of trust in Mei-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:13.80,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,N-Natsumi does?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:16.58,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,It sure doesn't look that way to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:17.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:23.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I feel like Mei-chan naturally leads the 1st and 2nd years and pushes them forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:27.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Just as Kanon-senpai said, Mei-senpai has been taking the lead in keeping everyone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:30.68,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Well, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:36.08,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,if I don't do it, everyone just does whatever they want, so I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:39.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's impressive that you can step up like that without hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:44.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,If it were me, I'd just leave the leadership stuff to Chi-chan or Ren-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:49.90,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mei-senpai was also very reliable when we were heading to the Music World.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:52.14,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh, I heard about that from Margarete-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You worked really hard, Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:58.56,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Back then, I just thought I'd try to be a bit more like Chisato-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.23,0:00:59.73,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:04.66,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,looking back, I think I was probably trying a little too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:06.08,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I think that is perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:11.83,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Seeing Mei-senpai work hard has the benefit of making Liella more positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:12.57,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I totally get that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:15.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It makes us feel like we can't afford to lose either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.93,0:01:16.43,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.24,0:01:18.48,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,You and the others, Kanon-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:20.88,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,No, no, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:24.20,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,There's no way you upperclassmen would lose to someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:25.86,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Don't say that, Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:28.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You just said "someone like me," didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.76,0:01:33.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You have more power to move those around you than you realize.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:36.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And you have the kindness to support others, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.48,0:01:37.41,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.41,0:01:39.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Margarete says it often as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:42.37,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,"I can't let myself be outdone by Mei-senpai."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:43.01,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,She says.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:45.84,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, that sounds like something she'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:50.42,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,By the way, your Margarete impression is spot on, Tomari.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:51.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I am flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:56.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Anyway, Mei-chan, you're the driving force of Liella, so we're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:58.52,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,The driving force?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.36,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Man, that feels like a bit of an exaggeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:07.20,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Well, if it's just about lighting a fire under the engine, I can do that anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That is very reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:15.38,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,In that case, please go ahead and light a fire under my sister's motivation for the next exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.38,0:02:16.07,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:16.69,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,that sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:19.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Then light a fire under my sweets-making too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:22.60,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,Don't get carried away, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:25.28,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,I can't look after you that much!
Comment: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:43.12,4,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Self-Introductions ===
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:43.12,4,host,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Girls' High School Broadcasting Club: Lieraji with Tomari, Kanon, and Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:50.29,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Hello,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.16,0:02:52.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:54.64,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I'm Date Sayuri, the voice of Shibuya Kanon!
Comment: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:57.28,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Self-Introductions ===
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:57.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm Sakakura Sakura, the voice of Onitsuka Tomari!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.96,Yabushima Akane,host,0,0,0,,And I'm Yabushima Akane,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.62,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,the voice of Yoneme Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:01.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Together, we are
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:03.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:06.43,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:12.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,So, this episode features Tomari, Kanon, and Mei. Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:11.30,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mei-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:13.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,welcome to the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:15.35,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Glad to have you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:16.57,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:25.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Today is March 24th, but coming up on March 28th, which is Sunny Pa Day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:30.30,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's the birthday of Hijirisawa Yuna's voice actress, Yoshitake-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:31.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:32.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Happy Birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:34.58,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Sunny Pa Day is actually Sunny Pa Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:35.90,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It must be fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:38.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's just too incredible. Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:37.97,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:39.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.16,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Let's all celebrate when the day comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:46.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Definitely. Now then, we've received some mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:42.98,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.05,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:47.64,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,I'll read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.28,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,This is from Liella name: Kabo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:55.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you! "Congratulations on being confirmed to perform at LuckyFes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:56.17,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Comment: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:05.08,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Self-Introductions ===
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:05.08,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Seeing Liella! perform in Ibaraki, which is both my hometown and the Onitsuka sisters' hometown, was one of my dreams."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:27.08,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"When I saw the announcement, my emotions exploded so much I almost screamed at work. Hitachi Seaside Park is full of memories for me, from school trips to BBQs with family and friends, so I'm so happy to make new memories there with Liella!."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:13.18,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:27.57,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:32.96,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I'm looking forward to having the best time ever with everyone in Liella! this summer."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:33.68,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:34.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:40.58,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,Next is from Liella name: Takashi from Sendai. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:41.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:50.28,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Congratulations on performing at LuckyFes! Since it's in Ibaraki, the home of the Onitsuka sisters, it must feel extra special."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:45.02,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:51.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:05:01.44,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Since it's a summer festival, please sweep the venue up in a whirlwind of excitement with your hot performance! I'm also excited to see if you'll perform any classic summer songs."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:57.70,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:01.97,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:09.72,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Oh, I'd love to hear about your enthusiasm for the festival or if there's anything specific you want to try doing at a summer fest!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:10.90,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,That was the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:11.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:12.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:17.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yes, Liella! will be performing at LuckyFes on Day 2, the 15th.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:21.14,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We've officially been confirmed to appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:21.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's official!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:23.58,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:24.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:25.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:30.16,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's great that it's in Ibaraki. You must be so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.08,0:05:28.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I really am!
Comment: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:35.24,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Self-Introductions ===
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:35.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really is the Onitsuka sisters' hometown, so we've always hoped that one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:37.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,we would be able to perform a live show in Ibaraki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:43.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I'm so happy it's coming true. And the other artists in the lineup are just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So amazing. It's a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:44.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:51.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was shocked. We'll do our best to show off Liella's power so we don't lose to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:47.78,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:54.16,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mhm. We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:53.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We look forward to seeing you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It'll be the middle of summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:56.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Since it's August 8th and 9th.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Make sure to eat well and stay healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:05:59.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Come visit us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:04.96,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Bring sports drinks. Should we perform while holding sports drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:02.82,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,While holding them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:05.26,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:05.95,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Should we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,They might go flying everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:07.94,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Flying everywhere, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:08.59,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:10.26,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We'd be so sticky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:13.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Our bodies would be covered in it. Even though it's a festival. It's too hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Even though it's a festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.78,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone, please come and have fun with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:19.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.62,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Alright everyone, please stay with us until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:28.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Broadcasting Station, Liella! Let's Super Star!
Comment: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:35.48,4,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Suggestion Box ===
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:35.48,4,host,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Broadcasting Station, Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:44.50,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,This is the Yuigaoka Girls' High School Suggestion Box, where we introduce your messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:48.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Alright everyone, let's say it together! One, two... Suggestion Box!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:50.88,Date Sayuri,host_meta,0,0,0,,Okay, let's read some mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,First, we have one from Liella name: Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:07:07.44,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you! They say, "I attended both days of the 7th Live in Kanagawa and watched the Aichi show via stream. Mei-chan's solo song, 'Sky Linker,' started by taking the baton from the club president, Chisato-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:08.06,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:20.80,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"What was especially striking was the part at the end of the chorus where you thrust your fist forward. Since it happened several times, I was so moved I almost cried the first time, and from the second time on, I was thrusting my fist along with you."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.10,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I totally get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:21.38,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:29.76,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It was a performance where I felt the full extent of Mei-chan's straightforward strength, including her big heart, the kindness that embraces weakness, and her desire to protect."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:30.64,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:31.78,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:33.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:36.36,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,Next is from Liella name: Baron Ojipan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:38.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:38.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:43.94,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Regarding the impressions of 'Sky Linker,' the clapping with your hands near your face..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:08:00.52,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"...and the side steps that followed looked like Flamenco, a traditional Spanish dance. Spain is often called the land of passion, and I felt you expressed Mei-chan's hidden passion through the dance. The moment I saw it, I thought, 'Whoa, that's so cool!'"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:49.82,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:01.56,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"That's how they felt."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:03.66,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Well then, Ciao."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.68,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"That's a Spanish parting greeting."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:06.80,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,(Laughs) That's what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:09.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you! Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:08.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:09.77,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Ciao!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:14.36,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,Alright, next is Liella name: Red-haired Kana. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:31.83,Sakakura Sakura,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Seeing 'Sky Linker' on Day 1 in Kanagawa was truly the best. Yabu-chan's dance was so cool I can't get it out of my head. The song and lyrics are great, so I listen to it constantly. I'd love to see the dance for 'Sky Linker' again somewhere!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:21.22,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:32.84,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,That's what they sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:33.98,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.65,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:36.21,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I want to hear more about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:52.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,'Sky Linker' was so cool. At first, I thought the performance might be done with a stand mic, just standing there and hyping up the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:42.02,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:52.90,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:56.14,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I couldn't really imagine you doing an intense dance to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:56.90,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:09:10.64,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I kept wondering how it would turn out, but I never expected Flamenco in the instrumental break. It was a really valuable experience, though. You don't usually get to do Flamenco.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:03.54,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:11.46,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:16.54,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,When I first saw the video of Mei-chan's choreography...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was like, "What is this dance?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:22.64,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Mei-chan was doing a style of dance that none of us had ever done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:29.58,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I said, "Oh, this is amazing!" and when I heard it was Flamenco, I was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:33.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was like, "How do you even do this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:32.70,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.64,0:09:34.74,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I couldn't do it at all at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:36.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,No way, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:42.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It used a core strength I'd never used before, and the whole foundation of the movement...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:47.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,How do I put it? The basics were totally different. I'm not an expert on dance or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:56.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but even so, it was so difficult I didn't understand it. I practiced just that instrumental part at home over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.02,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:57.58,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.00,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But you were so good at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:22.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It was incredibly cool. Since we all do our solo choreography lessons separately, we don't know when others are practicing or even if their songs involve dancing. When I'd see other members, I'd ask, "Wait, are you dancing to Kanon-chan's song?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:01.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That makes me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Or, "How much are you dancing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:26.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We had those kinds of conversations a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:32.98,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I happened to run into Yabu right after her choreography lesson,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:38.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,and she muttered something like, "I think it was Flamenco..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:43.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And I was like, "Wait, what do you mean?" I was so confused for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Like, "Flamenco?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:52.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Like Yabu said earlier, I expected her to just stand tall with a stand mic,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:57.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,with a sort of burning intensity. So when I heard Flamenco, I was like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:02.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I mean, you don't really get many chances to see Flamenco, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:03.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Liella! probably wouldn't do it normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:04.38,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Definitely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:12.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Not all of us together. It must be hard when you don't even know what the "correct" way looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:07.42,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:22.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It looks difficult just watching it, so I think it would've been a huge struggle if I had to do it. But I saw how hard you were practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:19.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's really tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:24.32,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, but your movements were so sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:34.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It was so cool. And like Miku-san said, that part where you thrust your fist forward felt so straightforward and very much like Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:26.66,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:31.11,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I love it.
Comment: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:35.56,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:35.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, I totally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:42.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's like, it's part of the choreography, but it doesn't feel like just a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:40.86,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:43.10,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:47.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It feels like you're throwing that punch with all your memories behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:12:09.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I found myself getting really emotional there too. That part at the end of the first and second chorus... and then the final chorus ends the same way. The movements are all identical, but for the first and second verses...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:53.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:13.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I could feel that the emotions packed into that final one were different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:20.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Even depending on the performance, I felt like what I was experiencing in that moment changed every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:25.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I put all my feelings into that fist. It was great, really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:24.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:26.51,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:31.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I really love the sound of the glass shattering. That part is so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:29.46,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:31.97,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:43.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,You can hear it even better during the live shows. It really resonates. And the flames in the background matched Mei-chan perfectly, it looked so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:34.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:41.97,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:47.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And then right after that, we had "Fantastic!" Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:47.86,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:48.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:53.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Since we were getting ready, I was watching Mei-chan's performance from the wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:59.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Feeling that heat, the two of us were like, "Alright, let's go! Let's keep this momentum going!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.42,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It was really, really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,You looked so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:11.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Can I say something too? Kanon performs right before Mei-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:19.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,and since there's a bit of time before Kanon's next turn, I was able to watch Mei-chan right as she was about to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:21.00,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I saw her from backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:31.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,And of course, there were times when I'd run into Mei-chan—or rather, Yabu—right after her performance ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:38.86,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Every time she finished, she had this incredible passion and a sense of having given it her all,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:43.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but at the same time, she always had this... how do I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:47.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yabu always had this look on her face like she was already thinking about what to do better next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,So, it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:56.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,She definitely felt a sense of accomplishment in her own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:14:00.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,but she also had this expression like, "Man, I've still got a long way to go."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:04.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Honestly, that just felt so much like Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:08.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was almost in tears while drinking my hot water,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:09.22,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,just watching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:11.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That is so Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:17.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,From our perspective, we're all thinking, "That was amazing!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:20.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But for her, it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:21.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:24.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The bar she sets for herself is just so high. But no, no, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:25.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone is like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:32.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone's desire to improve is so high, and we all share that mindset.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:38.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's why I get inspired to work harder too. It's a mutual influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:43.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,If it were just me, I might not have felt that way, but seeing everyone's performances,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:51.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I feel like, "Oh, I can go even further, there's more I can do." I think that's where it comes from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:53.30,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah. Wow, that's so true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:58.30,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, the solo songs this time really provided a lot of mutual inspiration. I felt it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:02.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone did. That's why I was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:14:59.54,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,For all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:03.57,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,For each other, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:04.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:11.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Even though a solo song is performed alone, in moments like this, you realize you're not actually alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:14.70,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I feel like we're all building it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:16.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Oh, and the outfits too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That "Girl Crush" style.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:19.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:21.82,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Man, I've never worn anything like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:23.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,It's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:28.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,But out of all of them, I think it looks the most like something you'd wear as everyday clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:36.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's simple and stylish enough that you wouldn't look out of place walking around town. People probably do wear stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:34.22,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:36.67,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,The fishnet tights were wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.38,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Honestly, that was a first for me in my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:42.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Wearing fishnets, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.64,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Is it okay for us to even be seeing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:47.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm just full of gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:47.83,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:59.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We were practically worshipping you backstage. We really were. Oh, and also, I think it was the final show, but during one of the last performances...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:50.16,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I was definitely worshipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:04.34,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Your hair got caught—it wasn't part of the choreo—and Kanon was either looking forward or looking down,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:09.04,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I forget which, but you did this gesture to brush it away,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:14.28,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,and the camera caught it perfectly. It was just so good, like, "Whoa!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:11.34,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's so embarrassing!
Comment: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.12,Sakakura Sakura,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.12,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I would definitely have that on repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:17.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Ah, it's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:19.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you, hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:21.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, it's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:24.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's like, "Whoa!" It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:24.02,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,So cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:26.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yabu-san doesn't remember it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.02,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Yabu-san has no memory of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But it was just so beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:34.24,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I loved it. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.36,0:16:32.86,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:34.71,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:40.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Everyone, please check it out. I'm sure some people are already saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:38.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,No, you really have to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Please remember it, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:44.10,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.38,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:49.32,Sakakura Sakura,host_meta,0,0,0,,Moving on, this one is from Liella name: Hajiketa Kata Popcorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.46,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:51.58,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:53.92,Date Sayuri,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Love Live! Superstar!! Liella! 7th LoveLive!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:02.30,0,host,0,0,0,,That was tough, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:09.86,0,host,0,0,0,,All of us in the 2nd and 3rd generation were saying this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:18.16,0,host,0,0,0,,but the choreography was incredibly difficult. It's the kind of difficulty
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:24.76,0,host,0,0,0,,that's hard for the audience to imagine. From the outside, it looks like
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:31.38,0,host,0,0,0,,we're having fun and dancing effortlessly, but it was actually brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:32.70,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It really was tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:34.98,0,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:40.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,When we first learned the moves, we all felt like our souls were leaving our bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:19:05.50,0,host,0,0,0,,We were all worried if we could actually sing and dance it at the same time. But as we practiced, we got in sync, and the anxiety turned into enjoyment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:19.88,0,host,0,0,0,,So on the day of the live, I felt more like I was enjoying the unity with the audience rather than being nervous. What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:18.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:35.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right. After "High Motivation" was announced, so many people were excited to see the performance, which felt like a lot of pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:44.76,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I actually thought the choreography would be a bit simpler or more relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:44.26,0,host,0,0,0,,I thought so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:45.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But there's so much dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Wait, why is it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:50.84,0,host,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:20:18.28,0,host,0,0,0,,I was worried we wouldn't be able to express the fun of the song. But as the live got closer, practice gave us confidence. We decided to just have fun and show the power of the 2nd and 3rd gens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:57.50,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:09.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:31.92,0,host,0,0,0,,In the end, we had fun, but at first, we couldn't even think about that. We were just desperate. When we first tried singing and dancing together...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:28.78,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:37.62,0,host,0,0,0,,We were all like, "This is impossible! This is seriously bad!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:48.60,0,host,0,0,0,,Since there were fewer of us than the full 11 members, we couldn't even find a moment to breathe. The formations were so complex too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:55.84,0,host,0,0,0,,And the rhythm wasn't just a simple 1-2-3-4 beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.84,0:21:03.48,0,host,0,0,0,,The choreographer had us hitting every tiny little sound in the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:11.00,0,host,0,0,0,,It turned out great, though. What part was the hardest for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:07.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:17.80,0,host,0,0,0,,Like Saku said, from the perspective of those watching, you're hitting every single beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:24.60,0,host,0,0,0,,But when you're just watching, you just end up thinking, "Wow, that looks fun!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:25.74,0,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:27.12,0,host,0,0,0,,So, which part was actually the toughest?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:30.86,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,With other songs, I can usually point to one specific part, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:38.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,For this song, every single part was a little bit difficult, so it felt like it was hard the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:36.04,0,host,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:38.93,0,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:40.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It was just... tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:46.68,0,host,0,0,0,,Usually, there are scenes where you're not singing and you just stand there watching the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:49.44,0,host,0,0,0,,but there was almost none of that in this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:50.98,0,host,0,0,0,,You're always doing one or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:22:00.96,0,host,0,0,0,,We were constantly moving. The formations were hard, but mostly it was just non-stop movement that left us breathless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:58.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:01.45,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:07.12,0,host,0,0,0,,I can say it now, but I was a mess when we were first learning the choreo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:08.51,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:09.85,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:13.62,0,host,0,0,0,,Seriously, everyone was crying while practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.62,0:22:15.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I was practically sobbing while doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.36,0:22:17.76,0,host,0,0,0,,I really wondered what was going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.40,0,host,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:28.72,0,host,0,0,0,,I thought Mei-chan would never cry, so seeing that made me cry even more. I don't even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:20.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:26.12,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,No, no, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:27.71,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.40,0:22:30.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Well, I can talk about it now that it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.36,0:22:43.08,0,host,0,0,0,,Everyone practiced so much at home. When we gathered again, the quality was on a whole different level. It was impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:46.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Wait, there's even a line in the lyrics about "having changed," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:51.82,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Hearing this story now, I feel like that's exactly what it was about.
Comment: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:56.44,Date Sayuri,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:56.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,I wasn't there because I was busy living my own life, but even the song title...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.44,0:22:58.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's called "High Motivation," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:22:59.79,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:06.80,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Like during the live show, the 2nd and 3rd years were shouting "High Motivation!" to pump themselves up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:08.44,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,They were really psyching themselves up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:12.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Seeing that just made me think, "Wow, they're so cool."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:18.20,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Exactly. It's the kind of song you can't get through unless you have that level of motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:25.32,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,But during the actual performance, everyone looked like they were having so much fun and smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.32,0:23:30.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It made me realize how much hard work must have gone into getting to that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:29.96,0,host,0,0,0,,Everyone worked so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:31.66,0,host,0,0,0,,Because everyone gave it their all,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:32.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,it turned out great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:37.12,0,host,0,0,0,,By the way, did you see Nako's impression? Maybe not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.64,0:23:36.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Wait, what impression?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:39.76,0,host,0,0,0,,You should have her show you sometime. Did you record a video?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:39.14,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:43.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,No, I didn't record it, but she's always mimicking the choreography for "High Motivation."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.96,0:23:49.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,It's so cute, so you should definitely have Nako show you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.24,0:23:49.86,0,host,0,0,0,,I want to see it! I want to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:53.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,She picks the most random parts. Oh, I really want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:52.68,0,host,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.40,0:23:56.60,0,host,0,0,0,,I wonder which part it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.60,0:23:59.40,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much. That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.92,0:23:58.64,0,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.16,0:24:10.84,0,host,0,0,0,,All right, we've talked a lot, but we still have more to say, so we'll keep talking next week. Anyway, thank you everyone for all the mail!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.80,0:24:07.30,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.96,0:24:11.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Comment: 0,0:24:12.16,0:24:18.88,0,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Lunchtime Request ===
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.16,0:24:18.88,0,host_meta,0,0,0,,Now, let's read a message for the Lunchtime Request. This one is from Liella name: Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.56,0:24:16.06,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.88,0:24:40.72,0,host,0,0,0,,Thank you. They say, "I'm requesting Sky Linker. My favorite part of the song is the 'Right now, I'll change it right now' line before the final chorus. Mei-chan usually speaks in a low voice, but her high notes here are so clear. I love the gap and how her voice sounds like a cry from the soul."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.00,0:24:20.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.72,0:24:42.12,0,host_meta,0,0,0,,That was the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.96,0:24:43.80,0,host,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.72,0:24:46.16,0,host,0,0,0,,You can really feel the soul in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.80,0:24:59.92,0,host,0,0,0,,It's a very passionate song, so please listen closely not just to the vocals, but to the backing track as well.
Comment: 0,0:24:59.92,0:25:01.82,0,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Lunchtime Request ===
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.92,0:25:01.82,0,host,0,0,0,,Now, please listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.82,0:25:03.88,0,host,0,0,0,,Yoneme Mei, "Sky Linker."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.16,0:25:10.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,The reason I only notice the broken pieces
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.32,0:25:18.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,is because I know what perfection looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.72,0:25:21.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,And that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.44,0:25:28.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'm far from a god who can end someone's hesitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.80,0:25:36.40,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,but I'll get soaked in the rain with you until we find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.68,0:25:42.36,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,My wish is in the blue sky, I'll take the hand that wants it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.08,0:25:47.74,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Everything, yes, I'll block out everything that's in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.74,0:25:50.68,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'll even protect you from fate itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.17,0:25:52.67,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Always,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.24,0:25:58.60,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,yes, always, don't lose to this depressing world today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.60,0:26:00.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Rise up
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.96,0:26:14.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,and fly over countless obstacles to reach our destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.76,0:26:18.28,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,We've become what you call "comrades."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.96,0:26:29.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,When I pray for someone other than myself, I'll prove there's not a single cloud of doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.04,0:26:35.72,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Dive into the blue sky, if you hold this hand, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.29,0:26:37.79,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.36,0:26:40.72,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,yes, everything—what's wrong with being weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.24,0:26:44.16,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,If you want to cry, then cry and scream, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.47,0:26:46.18,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Always,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.18,0:26:50.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,yes, always, I'll accept any version of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.96,0:26:51.88,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Show me who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.12,0:27:20.92,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Even if you're cracked, I'll show you I can take it all without breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.52,0:27:32.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,If you want a tough vessel, if you want a clear present, I'll change it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.80,0:27:34.04,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,In that blue sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.68,0:27:37.24,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,if you look up, I'll take you to that brilliant blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.81,0:27:39.31,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.88,0:27:42.56,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,yes, everything, I'll block out the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.56,0:27:45.52,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'll even protect you from fate itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.16,0:27:51.72,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,I'll support you, you have a place here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.52,0:27:53.48,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,Don't you ever lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.40,0:28:12.56,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Yuu-Yuu-Friendship Lunchtime Broadcast Station, Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.56,0:28:13.06,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Radio.
Comment: 0,0:28:16.00,0:28:19.00,0,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: News from Love Live! Superstar!! ===
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.00,0:28:19.00,0,host,0,0,0,,Announcements from Love Live! Superstar!!.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.24,0:28:21.42,0,host,0,0,0,,First, some music news.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.42,0:28:23.64,0,host,0,0,0,,On Wednesday, July 8th, the Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.64,0:28:27.24,0,host,0,0,0,,Musubu Project mini-album will be released.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.24,0:28:34.82,0,host,0,0,0,,We'll be releasing five versions: Original, Photo, Team Kids, Team Sports, and Team Green.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.82,0:28:41.94,0,host,0,0,0,,The Original, Team Kids, Team Sports, and Team Green editions feature new illustrations,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.94,0:28:45.26,0,host,0,0,0,,while the Photo edition features brand-new photos of the cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.26,0:28:52.44,0,host,0,0,0,,It'll include 4 songs, including a new group track, plus off-vocal versions for 8 tracks total.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.44,0:29:00.44,0,host,0,0,0,,First-press bonuses for the Original, Team Kids, Team Sports, and Team Green editions include member stickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.44,0:29:02.96,0,host,0,0,0,,The Photo edition will include a photo-booth style sticker.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.56,0:29:11.60,0,host,0,0,0,,All versions include a lottery application ticket for the Love Live! Series 15th Anniversary Love Live! Fes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.36,0:29:14.76,0,host,0,0,0,,Plus, as a bundle purchase bonus, you'll receive
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.76,0:29:16.62,0,host,0,0,0,,a Liella! sticker book.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.62,0:29:17.96,0,host,0,0,0,,Don't forget to pre-order!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.50,0:29:19.00,0,host,0,0,0,,To celebrate the release of the Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.00,0:29:24.20,0,host,0,0,0,,Musubu Project mini-album, we'll be holding a special handover event.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.72,0:29:29.20,0,host,0,0,0,,It'll take place over two days: Friday, October 2nd and Friday, October 9th.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.72,0:29:31.20,0,host,0,0,0,,Customers who pre-order or purchase the mini-album
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.20,0:29:38.40,0,host,0,0,0,,at participating stores will be entered into a lottery to attend the handover event.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.40,0:29:45.24,0,host,0,0,0,,The cast members vary by date, so please check the application details before applying.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.76,0:29:49.80,0,host,0,0,0,,Check the Love Live! Superstar!! official website for more details.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.68,0:29:53.83,0,host,0,0,0,,Next, news from the Love Live! Series Official Card Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.83,0:29:54.48,0,host,0,0,0,,The Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.48,0:30:02.78,0,host,0,0,0,,Start Deck featuring only Liella! members and songs will be released on Saturday, May 30th.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.78,0:30:08.68,0,host,0,0,0,,This product will include a special rarity "Secret Serial" card with a serial number.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.20,0:30:13.88,0,host,0,0,0,,Each numbered card is a super-luxurious, one-of-a-kind item in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.44,0:30:24.60,0,host,0,0,0,,The Start Deck has everything you need to play Loveca! right away, so if you haven't tried it yet, grab one and start playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.36,0:30:32.36,0,host,0,0,0,,Stay tuned for the latest updates on the official Love Live! website and official X account.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.08,0:30:34.22,0,host,0,0,0,,Now for some appearance info.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.22,0:30:35.84,0,host,0,0,0,,Starting April 1st, Liella!'s
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.84,0:30:36.68,0,host,0,0,0,,ChuChu Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.68,0:30:38.64,0,host,0,0,0,,Season 2 will begin airing on Nippon TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.16,0:30:43.04,0,host,0,0,0,,Haimashin No. 3 will continue as the program MC from Season 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.68,0:30:48.86,0,host,0,0,0,,Catch-up streaming will be available on TVer and Nittele Tada after the broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.86,0:30:50.04,0,host,0,0,0,,Be sure to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.64,0:30:54.96,0,host,0,0,0,,To commemorate the broadcast, the live concert Love Live! Superstar!! Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.96,0:30:55.88,0,host,0,0,0,,no ChuChu Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.88,0:31:02.34,0,host,0,0,0,,2026 will be held at LaLa arena TOKYO-BAY on August 1st and 2nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.34,0:31:10.02,0,host,0,0,0,,The second official lottery is open on Ticket Pia until 11:59 PM on Sunday, April 5th.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.02,0:31:11.80,0,host,0,0,0,,Please check that out as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.44,0:31:16.74,0,host,0,0,0,,For details on all the information shared today, please check the Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.74,0:31:21.56,0,host,0,0,0,,official X account and the Love Live! Superstar!! official website.
Comment: 0,0:31:21.56,0:31:23.32,0,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: News from Love Live! Superstar!! ===
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.56,0:31:23.32,0,host,0,0,0,,That's all for the announcements.
Comment: 0,0:31:33.16,0:31:35.68,0,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Closing ===
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.16,0:31:35.68,0,host,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Yu-Yu-Yu Friendship Lunchtime Broadcasting Station Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.68,0:31:38.46,0,host,0,0,0,,Radio. It's almost time to say goodbye for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.46,0:31:41.00,0,host,0,0,0,,Here is the information for our upcoming broadcasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.00,0:31:51.24,0,host,0,0,0,,For episode 266, scheduled for Tuesday, March 31st, we'll continue to have Yabushima Akane, the voice of Mei Yoneme, as our guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.24,0:32:02.22,0,host,0,0,0,,And for episode 267 on Tuesday, April 7th, we'll welcome Ookuma Wakana, the voice of Kinako Wakana, for a Tomari-Kanon-Shiki trio episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.22,0:32:04.44,0,host,0,0,0,,We're looking forward to your messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.44,0:32:07.24,0,host,0,0,0,,So, how did you enjoy today's broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.80,0:32:08.76,0,host,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.44,0:32:10.16,0,host,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.84,0:32:11.80,0,host,0,0,0,,Ding ding ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.64,0:32:13.48,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Wait, is it always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.89,0:32:15.39,0,host,0,0,0,,Ding ding ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.12,0:32:19.08,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Sakura, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.08,0:32:19.96,0,host,0,0,0,,Oh no, oh no, oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.96,0:32:21.84,0,host,0,0,0,,Saku, you actually surprised me just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.84,0:32:23.92,0,host,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to join in on that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.92,0:32:27.66,0,host,0,0,0,,I was thinking, "When did Sakura become like this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.96,0:32:27.68,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,She's genuinely worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.66,0:32:33.80,0,host,0,0,0,,I couldn't think of a comeback, so I figured I'd just roll with it instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.96,0:32:32.46,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.00,0:32:34.88,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.88,0:32:37.18,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Yabushima looked so confused just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.18,0:32:38.80,0,host,0,0,0,,Saku, she was worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.88,0:32:41.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Being pitied is the most embarrassing thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.96,0:32:44.26,0,host,0,0,0,,Anyway, how was it for you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.26,0:32:51.16,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Well, I got to share my thoughts in such great detail... or rather, I talked a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.76,0:32:52.66,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Was that really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.66,0:32:53.92,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.92,0:32:55.08,0,host,0,0,0,,I'm sure everyone wanted to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.76,0:32:58.72,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We'll be talking more next week, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.08,0:32:58.65,0,host,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.65,0:33:02.34,0,host,0,0,0,,I wonder how long we're allowed to keep talking about the 7th Live.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.34,0:33:06.78,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We're planning for about three years. Roughly, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.78,0:33:09.32,0,host,0,0,0,,We'll keep going until we've covered every single song.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.92,0:33:08.84,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Oh, then let's do every single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.52,0:33:11.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We won't be able to do the Unit Live at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.56,0:33:12.24,0,host,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.60,0:33:12.77,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,We'll push through!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.77,0:33:13.36,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Push through!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.36,0:33:13.86,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Push through!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.60,0:33:19.32,0,host,0,0,0,,Well then, this has been Love Live! Superstar!! Yu-Yu-Yu Friendship Lunchtime Broadcasting Station Liella!
Comment: 0,0:33:19.32,0:33:20.18,0,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Closing ===
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.32,0:33:20.18,0,host,0,0,0,,That is all for this episode.
Comment: 0,0:33:20.18,0:33:22.36,0,,0,0,0,corner,=== Corner: Self-Introductions ===
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.18,0:33:22.36,0,host,0,0,0,,Your hosts were Date Sayuri, the voice of Shibuya Kanon,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.36,0:33:24.60,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,Sakakura Sakura, the voice of Onitsuka Tomari,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.60,0:33:26.80,0,host,0,0,0,,and Yabushima Akane, the voice of Yoneme Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.40,0:33:27.96,Date Sayuri,host,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.72,0:33:36.64,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,In the breathtaking sunset, I heard you say "see you again."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.56,0:33:39.20,Sakakura Sakura,host,0,0,0,,The Gentle Breeze and You.
